# 🚀 PrepAI

PrepAI is a full-stack AI-powered interview preparation platform designed to help students and job seekers prepare for technical interviews. It combines AI mock interviews, resume analysis, DSA tracking, personalized study plans, company-specific roadmaps, and analytics into one modern application.

---

# ✨ Features

### 🎤 AI Mock Interviews
- AI-generated interview questions
- Role-specific interview sessions
- Voice & text interview mode
- Real-time answer evaluation
- Per-question scoring
- Comprehensive interview report

### 📄 Resume Analyzer
- AI-powered resume analysis
- ATS improvement suggestions
- Skill gap detection
- Resume enhancement recommendations

### 💻 DSA Tracker
- Track solved problems
- Difficulty-wise progress
- Topic-wise organization
- Performance statistics

### 📚 Company Roadmaps
Generate AI-powered preparation roadmaps for companies including:
- Amazon
- Google
- Microsoft
- Meta
- Adobe
- Flipkart
- Atlassian
- Goldman Sachs
- Uber
- Walmart Labs
- Infosys
- TCS

### 📅 Personalized Study Plans
- Weekly preparation schedules
- Customized learning roadmap
- Company-focused preparation
- AI-generated study strategy

### 📊 Analytics Dashboard
- Interview performance
- DSA progress
- Weekly analytics
- Overall preparation insights

### 🎙️ Voice Mode
- Speech Recognition
- Speech Synthesis
- Hands-free interview experience
- Browser-native Web Speech API

### 🔐 Authentication
- JWT Authentication
- Secure password hashing
- Protected routes
- Persistent login sessions

---

# 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Category | Technology |
|----------|------------|
| Frontend | React 18, Vite, Tailwind CSS |
| Routing | Wouter |
| State Management | TanStack Query |
| HTTP Client | Axios |
| Charts | Recharts |
| Icons | Lucide React |
| Backend | Node.js, Express.js |
| Database | MongoDB, Mongoose |
| Authentication | JWT, bcryptjs |
| AI | Groq + Gemini |
| Voice | Web Speech API |

