# 🐛 Common Issues

| Issue | Solution |
|-------|----------|
| MongoDB Connection Error | Ensure MongoDB is running and MONGO_URI is correct |
| Invalid JWT | Verify JWT_SECRET is configured properly |
| CORS Error | Ensure CLIENT_URL matches the frontend URL |
| AI Not Responding | Check your Groq or Gemini API keys |
| Voice Mode Not Working | Use Google Chrome or Microsoft Edge |

